: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"> Place your hands back on the floor and press through your palms to push your body back up to the starting position.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Repeat:</strong><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"> Lower back down and repeat the movement for the set number of reps.</span></li>\r\n</ol>', '', 'Bodyweight, Bodyweight', 12, 4, NULL, 'uploads/image/1730480541Screenshot_52.png', 'URL', 'server', 'https://youtu.be/po05Wyp4BM8', 'Y', '2024-11-01 17:02:21', 'uploads/thumb/17304805411730480541screenshot_52.png', 2, 'Chest', NULL, NULL, 2, 5),
(58, 7, 'Good morning', 'The positioning is the same as an RDL, originating from the hips.', '<ol style=\"color: #0e101a; background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">\r\n<li style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Set Up:</strong><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\" data-preserver-spaces=\"true\"> Position the bar in the back rack with your knees in a soft bend, keeping them locked in that position throughout.</span></li>\r\n<li style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt; list-style-type: decimal;\"><strong style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; margin-top: 0pt; margin-bottom: 0pt;\">Hinge at the Hips:</strong><span style=\"background-image: initial; background-position: initial; background-size: initial; background-repeat: initial; backgr